                                            STORY           
                                     
ONCE UPON a time in a forest there lived a Monkey who resided on a berry tree which was on a banks of a river.
In the river there was a crocodile and his wife . 
one day crocodile came to rest under the tree then monkey was kind some he offer berrys to the crocodile
and he loved the berry so many days pass and the crocodile and monkey became friends



